title: [Witch's Garden, Tip of the Cap]
description: Colorful towering mushrooms soar upwards from wide and woody stems.  Though most of their caps can't be seen from this vantage point, a few toppled fungi still proudly display their bright crimson and orange tops, each splashed with creamy white dots.  The earthy aroma of moist soil and mushrooms hangs heavy in the still, nightime air.

Colorful shriveled mushrooms soar upwards from wide and woody stems.  Though most of their caps can't be seen from this vantage point, a few toppled fungi still proudly display their bright crimson and orange tops, each splashed with creamy white dots.  The earthy aroma of moist soil and mushrooms hangs heavy in the still, nightime air.
